  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to rigorously assess a program designed to empower patient
      living with HIV, to improve their health care and health, and to reduce disparities.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Our project has four major aims:

        1. Assess improvement in patient empowerment

        2. Assess improvement in patients' receipt of evidence-based care

        3. Assess improvement in patients' health

        4. Assess reduction in disparities in empowerment
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
